<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-HK">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <meta name="color-scheme" content="light dark">
  <meta name="description" content="本平台提供台灣一番賞代購、代抽、代收與跨境轉送服務，所有抽選行為於台灣完成，香港地區僅提供商品領取與寄送。">
  <title>建立新代抽服務 - 管理後台 [TOKEN VERSION]</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css?v=token-1">
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <div class="container">
      <a href="/" class="site-logo">
        <img src="/img/mirai-3.png" alt="TMA台灣分部-未來飛翔">
      </a>
      <a href="/admin" class="back-link">← 返回後台</a>
      <h1>建立新台灣一番賞代抽服務</h1>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main class="container">
    <div class="wizard">
      <!-- Step 1: Basic Info -->
      <div class="wizard-step active" id="step1">
        <h2>基本資訊</h2>
        <form id="basicInfoForm" class="form-card">
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="title">服務標題</label>
            <input type="text" id="title" name="title" required placeholder="例如: 海賊王一番賞">
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="cover_image_url">封面圖片 (可選)</label>
            <input type="text" id="cover_image_url" name="cover_image_url" placeholder="https://... 或者選擇文件點擊上傳自動填充">
            <div style="margin-top: 8px; display:flex; gap: 8px; align-items:center; flex-wrap:wrap;">
              <input type="file" id="cover_image_file" name="cover_image_file" accept="image/*" style="flex:1; min-width:200px;">
              <button type="button" id="uploadCoverBtn" class="btn btn-secondary btn-sm">上傳封面</button>
            </div>
            <div id="uploadStatus" style="margin-top: 8px; font-size: 14px; display:none;"></div>
            <div id="coverPreview" style="margin-top: 12px; display: none;">
              <img id="coverPreviewImg" alt="封面預覽" style="width: 100%; max-height: 220px; object-fit: cover; border-radius: 12px; border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.08);">
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="description">描述</label>
            <textarea id="description" name="description" rows="3" placeholder="簡單描述這個代抽服務"></textarea>
          </div>
          <div class="form-row">
            <div class="form-group">
              <label for="total_boxes">總盒數</label>
              <input type="number" id="total_boxes" name="total_boxes" min="1" required placeholder="80">
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
              <label for="price_per_box">每盒價格 (HK$)</label>
              <input type="number" id="price_per_box" name="price_per_box" step="0.1" required placeholder="100">
              <small>前台會同時顯示 NT$（匯率可由環境變數 TWD_PER_HKD 調整）</small>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
              <label for="token_price_per_box">每盒 Token 價格 *</label>
              <input type="number" id="token_price_per_box" name="token_price_per_box" min="1" required placeholder="299">
              <small>客戶用 Token 買盒會按呢個價格扣除</small>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="form-row">
            <div class="form-group">
              <label for="num_pools">商品池數量 (分池最終賞)</label>
              <input type="number" id="num_pools" name="num_pools" min="1" value="1">
              <small>如果不分池請留 1</small>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="form-actions">
            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary btn-large">下一步: 新增商品</button>
          </div>
        </form>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 2: Add Items -->
      <div class="wizard-step" id="step2">
        <h2>新增商品</h2>
        <div class="item-management">
          <div class="current-items">
          <h3>已新增商品 (<span id="itemCount">0</span>)</h3>
          <div id="itemList" class="item-list-admin">
            <div class="empty-state">
              <p>尚無商品，請在右側新增</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="add-item-form">
          <h3>新增商品</h3>
          <form id="addItemForm" class="form-card">
            <div class="form-group">
              <label for="tier">獎級</label>
              <select id="tier" name="tier" required>
                <option value="A">A賞</option>
                <option value="B">B賞</option>
                <option value="C">C賞</option>
                <option value="D">D賞</option>
                <option value="E">E賞</option>
                <option value="F">F賞</option>
                <option value="G">G賞</option>
                <option value="H">H賞</option>
                <option value="LAST">LAST賞</option>
              </select>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
              <label for="item_name">商品名稱</label>
              <input type="text" id="item_name" name="item_name" required placeholder="例如: 路飛手辦">
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
              <label for="item_description">描述 (可選)</label>
              <textarea id="item_description" name="item_description" rows="2"></textarea>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
              <label for="image_url">圖片網址 (可選)</label>
              <input type="url" id="image_url" name="image_url">
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
              <label for="total_count">數量</label>
              <input type="number" id="total_count" name="total_count" min="1" required value="1">
            </div>
            <div class="form-group checkbox">
              <label>
                <input type="checkbox" id="is_final" name="is_final">
                這是最終賞
              </label>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group" id="poolNumberGroup" style="display: none;">
              <label for="pool_number">商品池編號</label>
              <input type="number" id="pool_number" name="pool_number" min="1" value="1">
              <small>最終賞屬於哪個商品池</small>
            </div>
            <div class="form-actions">
              <button type="button" id="addItemBtn" class="btn btn-primary">新增此商品</button>
              <button type="button" id="loadDefaultTemplateBtn" class="btn btn-secondary">載入預設一番賞商品 template</button>
            </div>
          </form>
        </div>
        </div>

        <div class="form-actions final-actions">
          <button type="button" id="backToStep1" class="btn btn-secondary">上一步</button>
          <button type="button" id="finishBtn" class="btn btn-success btn-large" disabled>完成建立</button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

  <footer>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="legal-footer" style="background: #f8f9fa; border-radius: 8px; padding: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; text-align: left; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6; color: #495057;">
        <strong>【服務聲明】</strong><br>
        <ol style="margin: 8px 0 0 20px; padding: 0;">
          <li>本平台僅提供日本／台灣一番賞商品之代購及代抽服務。</li>
          <li>所有抽選行為及相關交易均於海外（台灣）由當地合作單位完成，香港僅作為資訊展示及代購安排之平台，不涉及任何抽獎、博彩或機會遊戲活動之經營或操作。</li>
          <li>由於相關抽選活動並非於香港進行，本平台並不構成香港法例下之獎券、抽獎或賭博業務。</li>
          <li>用戶於下單時，即表示已年滿18歲，明白及同意抽選行為於海外進行，接受抽選結果之隨機性及不可預測性。</li>
          <li>所有商品內容、款式及中獎機率，均以當地官方公佈為準。基於抽選性質，所有訂單一經確認恕不接受退款或更換。</li>
        </ol>
      </div>
      <p>&copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Ichiban Kuji Proxy Service</p>
      <p style="margin-top: 8px; opacity: 0.7;">Powered by TMA台灣分部-未來飛翔</p>
    </div>
  </footer>

  <script src="/js/app.js?v=token-1"></script>
  <script>
    document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {
      initCreateRafflePage();
    });
  </script>
</body>
</html>
